{"title":"Wolf Tooth New Single Speed Cog Colors and Stainless Lockrings","link":"https://theradavist.com/wolf-tooth-new-single-speed-cog-colors/","date":1711546759000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_SS-cogs-and-spacers-kit_1.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_SS-cogs-and-spacers-kit_1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_SS-cogs-and-spacers-kit_1.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_SS-cogs-and-spacers-kit_1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_SS-cogs-and-spacers-kit_1.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Minnesota-based Wolf Tooth Components just announced a plethora of colors available for its <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=1f8f513b-b98b-4cf0-abf5-e477c8747e9c&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolftoothcomponents.com%2Fcollections%2Fsinglespeed\" target=\"_blank\">7075 aluminum single speed cogs</a> ($54.95) as well as <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=1f8f513b-b98b-4cf0-abf5-e477c8747e9c&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolftoothcomponents.com%2Fcollections%2Fsinglespeed\" target=\"_blank\">stainless steel lockrings and spacers</a> ($29.95)…<span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_SS-cogs-and-spacers-kit_5.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_SS-cogs-and-spacers-kit_5.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_SS-cogs-and-spacers-kit_5.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_SS-cogs-and-spacers-kit_5.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_SS-cogs-and-spacers-kit_5.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_SS-cogs-and-spacers-kit_7.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_SS-cogs-and-spacers-kit_7.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_SS-cogs-and-spacers-kit_7.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_SS-cogs-and-spacers-kit_7.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2024/03/Wolf-Tooth_SS-cogs-and-spacers-kit_7.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>These aluminum single speed cogs feature extra tall teeth for reliable chain retention when using chain tensioners. No more kicked chains. They are reversible and feature a 4.5 mm width at the base that won’t dig into your freehub body. They’re available in 16 to 22 tooth options, in blue, black, purple, gold, orange, and green.</p>\n<p><strong>Compatibility:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>These will fit on Shimano Hyperglide style freehub spline (geared or single speed).</li>\n<li>Not compatible with Shimano Microspline or SRAM XD freehubs.</li>\n<li>Designed to work with any chain through 12-speed</li>\n<li>Tooth width optimized for 9,10, and 11-speed chains</li>\n<li>Not compatible with Campagnolo Ekar 13-speed chains</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Wolf Tooth also has spacer kits with or without stainless lockrings.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatible with any 10 or 11-speed HG freehub body</li>\n<li>Kit includes two 1.5mm, three 5mm, and one 15mm aluminum spacers</li>\n<li>Spacers can be used in combination to achieve 45, 47.5, 49, 52, and 55mm chainlines</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Check out it all at <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=1f8f513b-b98b-4cf0-abf5-e477c8747e9c&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolftoothcomponents.com%2Fcollections%2Fsinglespeed\" target=\"_blank\">Wolf Tooth</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/wolf-tooth-new-single-speed-cog-colors/\">Wolf Tooth New Single Speed Cog Colors and Stainless Lockrings</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"803aa5ef5f7638bbecc3361dc5ddb31ea81d5c285b8bf75a7b54f776ed0a9cd3","category":"Cycling"}